TimeseriesDataset

public TimeseriesDataset(java.lang.String priceName,

                         int step,
                         org.jfree.chart.axis.SegmentedTimeline timeline,
                         java.util.TimeZone timeZone,
                         boolean createAverage)
Creates a new TimeseriesDataset instance.

参数：
priceName - the price chart name.
averageName - the average chart name.
volumeName - the volume chart name.
timePeriodClass - the TimePeriod class.
step - the step of the time period.
timeline - a "segmented" timeline.
timeZone - the time zone.
createAverage - indicates whether or not the average chart should be created.
